<li id="cite_note-Gass-12"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Gass_12-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFGass.2C_William_H.1957"><a href="/wiki/William_Gass" title="William Gass" class="mw-redirect">Gass, William H.</a> (1957). "The Case of the Obliging Stranger". <i>The Philosophical Review</i> <b>66</b>: 193–204. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F2182374" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F2182374" rel="nofollow">10.2307/2182374</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+Case+of+the+Obliging+Stranger&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Philosophical+Review&amp;rft.aulast=Gass%2C+William+H.&amp;rft.au=Gass%2C+William+H.&amp;rft.date=1957&amp;rft.volume=66&amp;rft.pages=193%E2%80%93204&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.2307%2F2182374&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Consequentialism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13" title="">^</a></b> Mullender, Richard (2000) 'Theorizing the Third Way: Qualified Consequentialism, the Proportionalty Principle and the New Social Democracy', <i>Journal of Law and Society</i> 27(4):493-516.</li>
<li id="cite_note-14"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14" title="">^</a></b> Page, James S. (2008) <i>Peace Education: Exploring Ethical and Philosophical Foundations.</i> Charlotte: Information Age Publishing. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781593118891" class="internal">ISBN 978-1-59311-889-1</a>. <a href="http://www.infoagepub.com/products/content/p478d75b79b1ea.php" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.infoagepub.com/products/content/p478d75b79b1ea.php" rel="nofollow">[3]</a><a href="http://eprints.qut.edu.au/12263/" class="external autonumber" title="http://eprints.qut.edu.au/12263/" rel="nofollow">[4]</a></li>
</ol>
</div>
<p><a name="Further_reading" id="Further_reading"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Consequentialism&amp;action=edit&amp;section=24" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
