<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFDarwall2002">Darwall, Stephen (Ed.) (2002). <i>Consequentialism</i>. Oxford: Blackwell. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780631231080" class="internal">ISBN 978-0-631-23108-0</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Consequentialism&amp;rft.aulast=Darwall&amp;rft.aufirst=Stephen+%28Ed.%29&amp;rft.au=Darwall%2C+Stephen+%28Ed.%29&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.place=Oxford&amp;rft.pub=Blackwell&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-631-23108-0&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Consequentialism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFHonderich.2C_Ted2009">Honderich, Ted (2003). <i><a href="http://www.ucl.ac.uk/~uctytho/ted9.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.ucl.ac.uk/~uctytho/ted9.htm" rel="nofollow">Consequentialism, Moralities of Concern and Selfishness</a></i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.ucl.ac.uk/~uctytho/ted9.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.ucl.ac.uk/~uctytho/ted9.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.ucl.ac.uk/~uctytho/ted9.htm</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Consequentialism%2C+Moralities+of+Concern+and+Selfishness&amp;rft.aulast=Honderich%2C+Ted&amp;rft.au=Honderich%2C+Ted&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ucl.ac.uk%2F%7Euctytho%2Fted9.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Consequentialism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFScheffler1994">Scheffler, Samuel (1994). <i>The Rejection of Consequentialism: A Philosophical Investigation of the Considerations Underlying Rival Moral Conceptions</i>. Oxford: Oxford University Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780198235118" class="internal">ISBN 978-0-19-823511-8</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Rejection+of+Consequentialism%3A+A+Philosophical+Investigation+of+the+Considerations+Underlying+Rival+Moral+Conceptions&amp;rft.aulast=Scheffler&amp;rft.aufirst=Samuel&amp;rft.au=Scheffler%2C+Samuel&amp;rft.date=1994&amp;rft.place=Oxford&amp;rft.pub=Oxford+University+Press&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-19-823511-8&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Consequentialism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
